BT /F1 10.50 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 279.50 Tm (Map is NOT a subtype of Collection. It stores key-value pairs rather than individual elements, which is) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 265.10 Tm (exactly why it lives in a separate hierarchy. Say this explicitly - it is a very common interview question.) Tj ET
