BT /F1 10.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 485.20 Tm (Definition of a List, then two panels: everyday operations on the left, a small performance table on the right.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 471.70 Tm (A yellow gotcha box at the bottom.) Tj ET
