BT /F1 10.50 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 112.60 Tm (The rule on screen: inherit for a genuine IS-A relationship; compose to reuse behaviour. Most of the) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 98.20 Tm (time, composition is the right answer.) Tj ET
