BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 343.50 Tm (the ends and doubles as a queue; Comparable defines natural order while Comparator is flexible.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 328.50 Tm (Sets: HashSet is fastest with no order, LinkedHashSet keeps insertion order, TreeSet keeps things) Tj ET
