BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 298.50 Tm (override hashCode and equals together for custom keys. Class relationships: IS-A is inheritance,) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 283.50 Tm (HAS-A is composition or aggregation, favour composition for reuse, abstract classes are partial) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 268.50 Tm (implementations while interfaces are pure contracts. File I/O: use BufferedReader and) Tj ET
